---
const alexQuote = '"I never thought I could master these techniques so quickly. The Part-Time Hypnotist didn\'t just teach me the skills; it gave me the confidence to use them immediately. A total game-changer for my career."';
---
<section class="section bg-slate-50">
  <div class="section-wide">
    {/* Featured case study — Kim */}
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center mb-16">
      <div>
        <img src="/images/26-proof-case-study-tree.png" alt="Kim, a kindergarten teacher who now earns $5k/month as a part-time hypnotist" class="rounded-xl shadow-xl w-full" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">
          Case Study: <span class="text-pth-blue">Kim, a kindergarten teacher</span>, who now earns an extra $5k a month as a Part-Time Hypnotist
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p>Kim first came to me because her daughter was experiencing extreme anxiety. They'd tried everything: therapy, medication, specialists… yet after just a few days of using these "rapid relief" tools on her daughter, Kim told me that she "was like a whole new person".</p>
          <p>She wanted me to train her so she could keep helping her daughter. Since she was part of the PTA association in her school, word quickly spread. She built up a reputation doing hypnosis on kids and teens. Now she makes a "second income" working only on weekends and an occasional weeknight session. This is money she uses to pay for luxury cruise, renovations, college funds, or a new car!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Alex J. testimonial slider — 5 identical cards as in the original */}
    <div class="my-12 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="flex gap-6 overflow-x-auto snap-x snap-mandatory pb-4 px-2 scrollbar-thin">
        {Array.from({ length: 5 }).map(() => (
          <blockquote class="snap-start flex-shrink-0 w-[90%] sm:w-[60%] lg:w-[40%] bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 md:p-8 border-l-4 border-pth-orange">
            <p class="italic text-base md:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">{alexQuote}</p>
            <footer class="mt-4 font-semibold text-pth-blue text-sm">
              — Alex J., Freelance Consultant<br />
              <span class="text-pth-orange">★★★★★</span>
            </footer>
          </blockquote>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Liz / Connie / Erin — image-paired short callouts */}
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-10 mt-12">
      Hear From <span class="text-pth-blue">More PTH Graduates</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <img src="/images/27-proof-case-study-foliage.png" alt="Liz" class="w-full" />
        <p class="p-6 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          <strong class="text-pth-blue">Liz</strong>, who started with the idea of seeing a few clients on the side of her career as a therapist and within a few months replaced her income!
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <img src="/images/28-proof-case-study-bestselling-book.png" alt="Connie" class="w-full" />
        <p class="p-6 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          <strong class="text-pth-blue">Connie</strong>, who now has a full-time practice where she splits her time between Austria &amp; Australia (to avoid the winters!)
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden p-6 flex items-center">
        <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          <strong class="text-pth-blue">Erin</strong> who started using this on her Nursing patients, and quickly filled her calendar with patients who became clients, then their families, then their friends…
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
